(5406, 'BLOCK_0XYPRRE381', 'image', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"image","priority":70,"contextInfos":[],"file":{"id":115,"title":[],"desc":{"fr_FR":"\\u00c9cole \\u00e9l\\u00e9mentaire Tamarin"},"fileUrl":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/4bb615fdbe1f.jpg","mimeType":"image\\/jpeg","ext":"jpg","thumb":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/thumb\\/thumb_4bb615fdbe1f.jpg","name":"4bb615fdbe1f.jpg","createdAt":"2020-06-16T12:30:00+0000","modified_at":"2020-06-19T08:55:00+0000","originalName":"ffbaea048710","useCount":null,"focus":{"x":null,"y":null}},"link":{"target":"_self","name":[],"anchor":"","type":4,"showTitle":true,"showDesc":true,"href":115}},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c2993"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3283),
(5407, 'BLOCK_WZIHK67JDJ', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c2999"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Le dernier trimestre a été&nbsp;<strong>aux couleurs des découvertes</strong>. Les élèves ont participé à plusieurs projets autour du thème du&nbsp;<strong>bien-être</strong>. Ils ont rencontré des professionnels, ont fait des sorties et ont clôturé l''année par de beaux spectacles.&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3283),
(5408, 'BLOCK_1XPBE33GQ1', 'image', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"image","priority":70,"contextInfos":[],"file":{"id":116,"title":[],"desc":{"fr_FR":"\\u00c9cole \\u00e9l\\u00e9mentaire Tamarin"},"fileUrl":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/fad9d8e66a64.jpg","mimeType":"image\\/jpeg","ext":"jpg","thumb":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/thumb\\/thumb_fad9d8e66a64.jpg","name":"fad9d8e66a64.jpg","createdAt":"2020-06-16T12:31:00+0000","modified_at":"2020-06-19T08:55:00+0000","originalName":"fc7441f2a371","useCount":null,"focus":{"x":null,"y":null}},"link":{"target":"_self","name":[],"href":116,"anchor":"","type":4,"showTitle":true,"showDesc":true}},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3011"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3284),
(5409, 'BLOCK_9V25NNZSJF', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3017"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Les élèves de&nbsp;Cm1&nbsp;ont eu le plaisir de faire&nbsp;<strong>une classe de découverte</strong>&nbsp;du 26 au 29 mars 2019 à Riambel.<br />\nUn grand merci à leurs enseignants et aux animateurs qui les ont accompagnés.&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3284),
(5410, 'BLOCK_DD7BVA550X', 'image', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"image","priority":70,"contextInfos":[],"file":{"id":117,"title":[],"desc":{"fr_FR":"\\u00c9cole \\u00e9l\\u00e9mentaire Tamarin","en_FR":"Elementary school Tamarin"},"fileUrl":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/3212ad952fe0.jpg","mimeType":"image\\/jpeg","ext":"jpg","thumb":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/thumb\\/thumb_3212ad952fe0.jpg","name":"3212ad952fe0.jpg","createdAt":"2020-06-16T12:31:00+0000","modified_at":"2020-06-24T06:01:00+0000","originalName":"29908fbb5749","useCount":null,"focus":{"x":null,"y":null}},"link":{"target":"_self","name":[],"href":117,"anchor":"","type":4,"showTitle":true,"showDesc":true}},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3028"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3285),
(5411, 'BLOCK_87B1TTSN2H', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3034"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p><strong>Le premier centre de vacances</strong>&nbsp;a eu lieu à l''école Paul et Virginie, du 25 Février au 01 Mars 2019,<br />\nsur le thème du carnaval.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3285),
(5412, 'BLOCK_53OWIB338E', 'image', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"image","priority":70,"contextInfos":[],"file":{"id":122,"title":[],"desc":{"fr_FR":"\\u00c9cole \\u00e9l\\u00e9mentaire Tamarin"},"fileUrl":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/817f728249ac.png","mimeType":"image\\/png","ext":"png","thumb":"\\/ressources\\/images\\/thumb\\/thumb_817f728249ac.png","name":"817f728249ac.png","createdAt":"2020-06-16T12:43:00+0000","modified_at":"2020-06-19T08:56:00+0000","originalName":"deecbf0cd33b","useCount":null,"focus":{"x":null,"y":null}},"link":{"target":"_self","name":[],"anchor":"","type":4,"showTitle":true,"showDesc":true,"href":122}},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3045"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3286),
(5413, 'BLOCK_MQ5281GAIL', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3051"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Les élèves de&nbsp;<strong>CM2</strong>&nbsp;ont visité les locaux de la&nbsp;<strong>MBC</strong>&nbsp;(Mauritius&nbsp;Broadcasting&nbsp;Corporation) dans le cadre du cours d''&nbsp;<strong>EMILE</strong>&nbsp;(dispensé en anglais)&nbsp; sur les médias.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3286),
(5414, 'BLOCK_5JU7TZVC2G', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":6,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3287),
(5415, 'BLOCK_22G2KA1G1V', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3074"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Le vendredi 25 janvier, le&nbsp;<strong>English Day</strong>&nbsp;a été célébré à l''école. Accompagnés de leurs enseignantes d''anglais, les élèves ont présenté des chants, offert des lectures aux plus petits et découvert les coutumes des pays anglophones.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3287),
(5416, 'BLOCK_U1DDLVVOHE', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":7,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3288),
(5417, 'BLOCK_476I9CKXJB', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3091"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>La deuxième semaine des&nbsp;<strong>lycées français du monde</strong>, s''est déroulée du 18 au 23 Novembre.<br />\nLes classes ont chanté&nbsp; dans les différentes langues présentes à l''école .</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3288),
(5418, 'BLOCK_K1MLLBH3CY', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":49,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3289),
(5419, 'BLOCK_0EZGA9MS90', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3107"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Les classes de CM2 ont encadré les classes de GS et CP pour le&nbsp;<strong>premier rallye maths</strong>&nbsp;de l''année.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3289),
(5420, 'BLOCK_ERB38SP8MV', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":50,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3290),
(5421, 'BLOCK_Z3AJQPXELL', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3123"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Séquence émotion lors de la commémoration du centenaire du&nbsp;<strong>11 novembre</strong>, élaborée et présentée&nbsp;<strong>par les élèves de CM1.</strong></p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3290),
(5422, 'BLOCK_0VAMLFLOJG', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":51,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3291),
(5423, 'BLOCK_TH29RAU70S', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3144"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Cette année, les classes de CM2 des&nbsp;<strong>4 écoles</strong>&nbsp;à programme français (Lycée La Bourdonnais, Ecole du Nord , Ecole Paul et Virginie et l’Ecole du Centre) se sont retrouvés à l''école du centre pour participer au&nbsp;<strong>cross 2018-2019</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3291),
(5424, 'BLOCK_RIB1TMNJAR', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":8,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3292),
(5425, 'BLOCK_SPZTSR7226', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3161"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p><strong>La semaine du goût</strong>&nbsp;s''est déroulée du&nbsp;<strong>08 au 12 octobre 2018</strong>, pilotée par les&nbsp;classes de <strong>maternelles</strong>.Une semaine autour des couleurs et du partage, qui a&nbsp; donné lieu à des moments, des sorties et surtout des&nbsp;<strong>découvertes uniques</strong>.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3292),
(5426, 'BLOCK_G4CGT6EMAW', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":9,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3293),
(5427, 'BLOCK_8ZG6B0MQPV', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3177"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>La classe de&nbsp;<strong>CE2-2</strong>&nbsp;a marché sur les pas du célèbre aviateur&nbsp;<strong>Rolland Garos.</strong></p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3293),
(5428, 'BLOCK_BABEO0KR8C', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":10,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3294),
(5429, 'BLOCK_LD907TBUPA', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3193"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Les fêtes de fin d''annéeà<br />\nl''école Paul et Virginie.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3294),
(5430, 'BLOCK_XSCBM71Q27', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":11,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3295),
(5431, 'BLOCK_XBWU4RSB79', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3214"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Samedi 22 septembre, 12 élèves de l''école de cm1 et de cm2 ont représenté l''école Paul et Virginie lors de la rencontre amicale de cross organisée par&nbsp;<strong>West Coast International Primary School.</strong> Nos élèves sont arrivés 2e sur 8 écoles primaires. Bravo aux élèves pour leur performance.&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3295),
(5432, 'BLOCK_59HMM9M6L6', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":12,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3296),
(5433, 'BLOCK_FX19EJOF4N', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c3231"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Le vendredi 21 septembre, les élèves de cm2 ont bénéficié d''une sensibilisation à la&nbsp;<strong>sécurité routière</strong>&nbsp;grâce à la présence du&nbsp;<strong>Kolektif Rivier Nwar et de la police</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>sous la forme d''une conférence suivie d''un parcours en vélo.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3296),
(5434, 'BLOCK_9PFJDY3B3A', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":13,"design":3,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3297);
