(5838, 'BLOCK_RHYEEBKN4J', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c8860"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p><strong>The priority of the school is&nbsp;to bring out the best in each of our students and to strive for excellence.</strong></p>\n\n<p>In each class,&nbsp;differentiated pedagogy&nbsp;is practised by a qualified teaching team.</p>\n\n<p>However, for some students this is not enough;&nbsp;and therefore, we&nbsp;implement additional protocols&nbsp;for students with special needs.&nbsp;These aids are set up, with the agreement of the student''s family, as recommended by the class teacher and the management.&nbsp;In addition to the class teacher and the headmistress, the following staff participate in the follow-up of these students:</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3536),
(5839, 'BLOCK_M7HN5J47S7', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c8866"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Annabelle Henri, the school nurse</strong> is available during school hours. In collaboration with the director, she develops Individualized Reception Projects to accommodate students with health problems.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3536),
(5840, 'BLOCK_KGJFN31W7C', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c8871"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p><strong>Louis Baxellerie, a qualified special needs teacher</strong>, is responsible for the ''Unité pour l''Inclusion Scolaire’ (also referred to as ULIS) which was set up in 2017. Mrs. Joelle Meunier is the class assistant.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3536),
(5841, 'BLOCK_VXA89SDVW8', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":36,"design":6,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3537),
(5842, 'BLOCK_VMKRS2J598', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c8896"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":"emphasis"}]', '<p style="text-align:center">Three therapists facilitating the care of your children consult within the school.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3538),
(5843, 'BLOCK_7F96ITW8H8', 'button', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"ButtonOption","priority":70,"text":"See table","link":{"target":"_blank","href":"..\\/ressources\\/fichiers\\/8de69ce6825e.pdf","anchor":"","type":1,"name":null}},{"optionType":"ButtonStyleOption","priority":80,"size":"medium","buttonAlignment":"align-center","textAlignment":"text-center"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3538),
(5844, 'BLOCK_1KRH544PUO', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c9713"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":"paragraph"}]', '<h2>A SPORT ORIENTATED SCHOOL</h2>\n\n<p>Students have at least two hours of sports a week either with their class teacher or the sports teacher Alicia Lamusse.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Several sports projects are organised each year such as: the GS / CP sports day (organised by the CM2 students), the French schools cross country event (the CM2 students), a sailing class, a kayaking class...</p>\n\n<p>Each student participates in a minimum of 8 swimming sessions per year at the Riverland Club pool.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3539),
(5845, 'BLOCK_B72BX088B5', 'gallery', NULL, NULL, '[{"fileGroup":37,"design":6,"optionType":"gallery"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3540),
(5846, 'BLOCK_ALMUBC8M7E', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c9746"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<h2>ARTS AT THE SCHOOL</h2>\n', NULL, '[]', 3541),
(5847, 'BLOCK_6RDSGJRUP3', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c9752"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', '<p>Students benefit from an artistic education which is included in our school program. &nbsp;Many projects are carried out during the year.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For example, our CE2 students participate in inter-school choir events.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For the last two years, an Arts Week has been organised within the school.<br />\nThis is an opportunity for all students to meet and discover local artists, as well as take part in art projects.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>See below a video from Arts Week 2017 (right)</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3541),
(5848, 'BLOCK_XO4GP75L1Q', 'video', NULL, NULL, '[{"priority":70,"optionType":"videoInfo","_id":"autoplay6244","provider":"vimeo","movieUrl":"https:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/video\\/236262887","url":"https:\\/\\/vimeo.com\\/236262887","params":"?\\u0026color=b91f1f"},{"priority":80,"optionType":"videoStyle","controlPanel":"Always","info":false,"branding":false,"color":"DARK"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3542),
(5849, 'BLOCK_WVQ8WMQFBK', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c9779"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":"emphasis"}]', '<p style="text-align:center">We remain at your disposal for any questions.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 3543),
(5850, 'BLOCK_WOX1CF0R0Q', 'button', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"ButtonOption","priority":70,"text":"Contact us","link":{"target":"_self","name":"Contact us","href":10,"anchor":"","type":0,"lang":"en_FR"}},{"optionType":"ButtonStyleOption","priority":80,"size":"medium","buttonAlignment":"align-center","textAlignment":"text-center"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":""}]', NULL, NULL, '[]', 3543),
(6583, 'BLOCK_VZQT61L6P4', 'text', NULL, NULL, '[{"optionType":"colors","priority":80},{"optionType":"effects","priority":90,"_id":"c7985"},{"optionType":"advancedCSS","priority":200,"cssClasses":"paragraph"}]', '<h2>An establishment with French programs</h2>\n\n<p>The Paul and Virginie School is also part of the local network of French Program Establishments in Mauritius which includes the North School in Mapou, the Center School and the Lycée des Mascareignes in Moka, the Lycée Labourdonnais in Curepipe and Paul and Virginie school. Regular educational actions are carried out with them in order to strengthen ties.</p>\n\n<p>Regular contacts are made between the Paul and Virginie School, the <a data-link-type="external" href="http://www.ambafrance-mu.org/" target="_blank">French Embassy in Mauritius</a> and its <a data-link-type="external" href="http://mu.ambafrance.org/Service-de-Cooperation-et-d-Action-Culturelle" target="_blank">Cooperation and Cultural Action Service</a>. A Steering Committee of the French Program Establishments in Mauritius is regularly convened by the Ambassador of France, who chairs it.</p>\n\n<p>By tripartite agreement, students leaving the Paul and Virginie School at the end of the elementary course are welcomed as of right in the 6th class at the Center School (Pierre poivre College) or at the Lycée Labourdonnais, at the choice of families.</p>\n', NULL, '[]', 4031),
