(11953, 'BLOCK_2SX6O5S49N', 'html', NULL, NULL, '[{"priority":70,"optionType":"html","html":"\\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022container\\u0022\\u003E\\n    \\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022row\\u0022\\u003E\\n        \\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022columns large-24 medium-24\\u0022\\u003E\\n            \\u003Cdiv id=\\u0022testimonial-slider\\u0022 class=\\u0022owl-carousel\\u0022\\u003E\\n                \\n                \\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022testimonial\\u0022\\u003E\\n                    \\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022pic\\u0022\\u003E\\n                        \\u003Cimg src=\\u0022..\\/ressources\\/images\\/ff2bc186810e.jpg\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022\\u003E\\n                    \\u003C\\/div\\u003E\\n                   \\n                    \\u003Cp class=\\u0022description\\u0022\\u003E\\n                       Our school is a non-profit organization that operates through its own funds and through donations. Our Management Committee is entirely made up of volunteers.\\n                    \\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\n                     \\u003C!--\\u003Ch3 class=\\u0022testimonial-title\\u0022\\u003E\\n                        All Volunteers\\n                    \\u003C\\/h3\\u003E--\\u003E\\n                \\u003C\\/div\\u003E\\n                \\n                \\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022testimonial\\u0022\\u003E\\n                    \\u003Cdiv class=\\u0022pic\\u0022\\u003E\\n                        \\u003Cimg src=\\u0022..\\/ressources\\/images\\/396c7d330440.jpg\\u0022 alt=\\u0022\\u0022\\u003E\\n                    \\u003C\\/div\\u003E\\n                   \\n                    \\u003Cp class=\\u0022description\\u0022\\u003E\\n                      We awaken each child\\u0027s desire to learn through our exceptional school environment.                    \\u003C\\/p\\u003E\\n                     \\u003C!--\\u003Ch3 class=\\u0022testimonial-title\\u0022\\u003E\\n                       Varied and Effective Teaching Programs\\n                    \\u003C\\/h3\\u003E--\\u003E\\n             